{"tid":1181190,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"遙距工作稅制問題","createTime":"2019-06-01T11:58:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-02T06:55:12.000Z","uid":66106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"57a7d013727b2b3dc0c5624be2911e03a1f64edf","tid":1181190,"uid":66106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T11:58:47.000Z","msg":"呢排睇緊啲Remote職位<br />\n假設如果我搵到份英國公司既工，出英磅，但係全時間都喺香港做野，咁交稅係咪剩係需要交英國嗰邊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c32e730288b3f3737734e63733eafbc1a55d151","tid":1181190,"uid":66106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T12:07:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a2be36bc8ad5e5ff5e770625c9b042c87fa0247","tid":1181190,"uid":19541,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T12:09:29.000Z","msg":"去睇DTA"},{"pid":"18e5be24e5ccfee4a41acb02f3f1d0e54e2c8982","tid":1181190,"uid":66106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2a2be36bc8ad5e5ff5e770625c9b042c87fa0247","tid":1181190,"uid":19541,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T12:09:29.000Z","msg":"去睇DTA"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T12:13:10.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">香港採用地域來源徵稅原則，香港居民只須就源自香港的收入 / 利潤繳稅，而源自香港以外的收入 / 利潤，則一般無須在香港課稅。因此，一般而言，香港居民沒有雙重課稅的問題。</span><br />\n<br />\n唔該哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb9a17c616f31de802513952c9d205a751dc2cc2","tid":1181190,"uid":93379,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T12:36:49.000Z","msg":"交唔交香港稅要睇三個factors 睇你source of income<br />\n<br />\n1. Contract係邊度簽/effect<br />\n2. 僱主office係邊<br />\n3. 邊度出糧<br />\n<br />\n如果最尾決定係hk source employment 全部都交香港稅<br />\n<br />\n如果係non hk source employment, 就用time apportionment 交稅<br />\n<br />\n利申：準備6月尾考tax<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f030bb21cace541fda8f6740dbbbdcdcc7882b9f","tid":1181190,"uid":66106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bb9a17c616f31de802513952c9d205a751dc2cc2","tid":1181190,"uid":93379,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T12:36:49.000Z","msg":"交唔交香港稅要睇三個factors 睇你source of income<br />\n<br />\n1. Contract係邊度簽/effect<br />\n2. 僱主office係邊<br />\n3. 邊度出糧<br />\n<br />\n如果最尾決定係hk source employment 全部都交香港稅<br />\n<br />\n如果係non hk source employment, 就用time apportionment 交稅<br />\n<br />\n利申：準備6月尾考tax<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T06:55:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過按照Exemption既D Part解釋，應該同Double Tax Relief一致，可以括免<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}